[normal]H
[normal]).
[normal]  The IFH is a not for-profit non government agency which is working to develop and promote a science-based approach to hygiene/infection prevention in home and everyday life settings.  Registered Charity No:CH-660 2131998-6
[normal]This submission addresses the following question:
[normal]What are the strengths and weaknesses of the Government’s 2013-2018 strategy for tackling antimicrobial resistance? What changes might be made to further strengthen the Government’s action plan?
